OL,3,CMan jailed for revenge arson attack on
OL,4,Cwrong house
OL,6,FA man who chose the wrong house and
OL,7,Fleft a complete stranger terrified in
OL,8,Fa revenge arson attack has been jailed.
OL,10,FThirty-year-old Wayne McDonald was
OL,11,Fheard by the victim knocking on the
OL,12,Fdoor of her Carlisle home late on 18
OL,13,FNovember 2023.
OL,15,FCarlisle Crown Court heard that she
OL,16,Fwatched on doorbell video footage as
OL,17,FMcDonald approached and tried the
OL,18,Fhandle.
