OL,6,FAs he sparked a lighter, the occupant
OL,7,Fassumed he was having a cigarette.
OL,8,FMcDonald walked away briefly but then
OL,9,Freturned and stuffed toilet roll which
OL,10,Fhad been set alight through the
OL,11,Fletterbox.
OL,13,FThis was extinguished but while damage
OL,14,Fwas limited, the court heard the
OL,15,Fpsychological impact of the arson
OL,16,Fattack was not.
