OL,3,CMan jailed for revenge arson attack on
OL,4,Cwrong house
OL,6,FMcDonald, of Harris Crescent,
OL,7,FCarlisle, admitted arson being
OL,8,Freckless as to whether life was
OL,9,Fendangered or property destroyed.
OL,11,FHe further admitted two breaches of a
OL,12,Frestraining order he had been given as
OL,13,Fpart of a suspended prison sentence
OL,14,Flast September.
OL,16,FHours before the arson attack,
OL,17,FMcDonald had left a note on his former
OL,18,Fpartner's vehicle and during a
OL,19,Fseparate incident shouted at her,
OL,20,Fcausing her to feel scared.
