OL,6,FFor the three offences, he was given a
OL,7,Ftotal prison sentence of two years and
OL,8,F11 months.
OL,10,FRecorder Brian Whitehead told McDonald
OL,11,Fof the arson offence: "This was
OL,12,Feffectively a revenge attack, albeit
OL,13,Fon the wrong person."
